      <title>中国大亨因诈骗投资者 10 亿美元面临美国审判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-23/chinese-tycoon-faces-us-trial-over-1-billion-investor-swindle</link>
      <description><![CDATA[流亡的中国亿万富翁郭文贵的审判本周在纽约开始，他被指控通过一项复杂的欺诈计划从投资者那里骗取超过 10 亿美元，该计划使他获得了包括价值 2600 万美元的新泽西豪宅和一艘价值 3700 万美元的游艇在内的奢侈品。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-23/chinese-tycoon-faces-us-trial-over-1-billion-investor-swindle</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国拨出创纪录的 190 亿美元用于推动芯片制造</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-23/south-korea-sets-aside-record-19-billion-to-boost-chip-industry</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国公布了一项价值 190 亿美元的一揽子激励措施，以支持其芯片行业，这对三星电子公司和 SK 海力士公司来说是一个福音，因为它们在竞争日益激烈的行业中竞相保持领先地位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-23/south-korea-sets-aside-record-19-billion-to-boost-chip-industry</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 02:39:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>恒大电动汽车部门面临最新打击，要求偿还补贴</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-23/evergrande-s-ev-arm-chased-to-repay-subsidies-in-latest-blow</link>
      <description><![CDATA[陷入困境的房地产开发商中国恒大集团的电动汽车部门因未能开始量产其备受期待的汽车而遭到地方政府追讨 19 亿元人民币（2.62 亿美元）的补贴。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-23/evergrande-s-ev-arm-chased-to-repay-subsidies-in-latest-blow</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 02:11:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国央行维持现状并暗示转向可能被推迟</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-23/bank-of-korea-holds-policy-steady-as-economic-growth-picks-up</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国央行保持货币政策稳定，并表示可能会在一段时间内保持紧缩政策，因为在出​​口增长和消费弹性的支撑下，经济增速超出预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-23/bank-of-korea-holds-policy-steady-as-economic-growth-picks-up</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 00:51:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
